# .zprofile - sourced once at login
#
# Keep this file quiet. Automation tools such as Codex use non-interactive
# login shells (`zsh -lc`), so stdout/stderr here corrupts command results.
#
# Shared PATH, command wrappers, and Codex-safe `mise` bootstrap live in
# `.zshenv`; interactive-only setup stays in `.zshrc`.
